===Proper noun===
'''Epimetheus'''
{{wikipedia}}
# (''Greek mythology''): son of [[Iapetus]] and [[Clymene]], brother to [[Atlas]] and [[Prometheus]], of whom he ignored warnings to beware of any gifts from [[Zeus]].  He accepted [[Pandora]] as his wife, thereby bringing sorrow to the world; father to [[Pyrrha]].